<div>Joshua Holt is the coordinator of the IBC program and teaches the Organizational Effectiveness portion of the course.&nbsp; Brother Holt has taught business at Ricks College and BYU-Idaho for 30 years and is one of the most experienced professors in the business department.</div>
<h2>&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>
<h2></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><a href="http://web.byui.edu/Directory/Employee/andrewsc">Chris Andrews</a>&nbsp;<img alt="Chris Andrews" height="142" src="Images/Colleges_and_Departments/Business and Communication/Business Management/andrewsc.jpg" style="float: left; border: black 5px solid;" width="100" /></h2>
<div>Chris Andrews teaches the Finance portion of the IBC.&nbsp; He has been with BYU-Idaho since 2001.&nbsp; Before coming to BYU-Idaho, Brother Andrews worked for 14 years in the business finance sector focusing on the areas of corporate finance and venture capital.</div>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<h2></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><a href="http://web.byui.edu/Directory/Employee/clarkm">Michael Clark</a>&nbsp;<img alt="Michael Clark" height="142" src="Images/Colleges_and_Departments/Business and Communication/Business Management/clarkm.jpg" style="float: left; border: black 5px solid;" width="100" /></h2>
<div>Michael Clark teaches the Product and Operations Management portion of the IBC.&nbsp;&nbsp;In 2005&nbsp;he came to BYU-Idaho&nbsp;from Intel where he was project manager for leading efficiency and cost savings efforts at the global brand leader for five years.</div>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<h2><a href="http://web.byui.edu/Directory/Employee/eagard">Drew Eagar</a>&nbsp;<img alt="Drew Eagar" height="142" src="Images/Colleges_and_Departments/Business and Communication/Business Management/eagard.jpg" style="float: left; border: black 5px solid;" width="100" /></h2>
